{"id":232531789,"title":"省電萬用充電器詢問","content":"大家有用過萬用電器嗎？\nhttp://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDE.jpg\n\n昨天FB看到侯以理介紹台達品牌Innergie一款萬用充電器lnnergie 45H \n介紹可以充筆電 手機 平板一堆3C一打多 \n以後用3C不用買那麼多個充電器製造一堆充電器垃圾 \n這種設計概念感覺還不錯 \n而且有高於業界的92%效能轉換率 避免一些能源浪費 \n現在才知道原來選充電器也可以顧到省電\n\n之前聽科技業哥哥講台達這家產品設計蠻注重環保   \n這次還有舉辦充電器回收的活動 \n舊換新買這個或其他一樣是萬用充電器系列的可以打85折 有點心動\n不知有人用過這種產品？\n如果可以撐很久的應該會想用用看，\n也順便回收家裡一堆無法再用的舊充電器","excerpt":"大家有用過萬用電器嗎？昨天FB看到侯以理介紹台達品牌Innergie一款萬用充電器lnnergie 45H，介紹可以充筆電 手機 平板一堆3C一打多，以後用3C不用買那麼多個充電器製造一堆充電器垃圾，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-19T11:07:00.029Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-19T11:07:00.029Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["充電器","省電","環保","愛地球","無痕"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"淡江大學","department":"統計學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDE.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"e6c113ce-3a53-4428-8d90-dfdd92220d0a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDEl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDEl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDEl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-19T11:07:00.029Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-19T11:07:00.029Z"},{"id":"e6c113ce-3a53-4428-8d90-dfdd92220d0a","url":"http://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDE.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/hoDrBDE","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hoDrBDEl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-19T11:07:00.029Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-19T11:07:00.029Z"}],"postAvatar":""}